{"tid":46474,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以明白我嘅感覺","createTime":"2016-12-19T16:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T17:27:22.000Z","uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd954795dd15ccbb9b9a28d93d6813c610606ec","tid":46474,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 我老豆老母乜都可以嘈一聲（最主要係老母挑起罵戰）小至玩電話大至話我老豆出去玩<br />\n仲要下下嘈完就要話離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱我老豆話未沖涼 我老母又嘈話佢唔理佢 佢唔叫就唔會沖又話有冇理過佢感受<br />\n有時屌屌下仲可以屌埋我落水 亦試比佢嘈交嘈醒左<br />\n真係好撚辛苦 成日都話冇人理佢話我老豆唔愛佢<br />\n我叫佢唔好諗咁多又可以話返我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794928f00112eb89a08565c4ada033a63c0fcc66","tid":46474,"uid":13176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:40:04.000Z","msg":"伯母係咪控制慾好強、好冇安全感既人？"},{"pid":"df07825f63de78021b14a2d40606146421a28ef3","tid":46474,"uid":47045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"50c4c82c38a739d360faf377019109de32f07213","tid":46474,"uid":47045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n自膠㩒錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪更年期？情緒難控制"},{"pid":"adb929beeb6bea584498e76179a2e12b9aeb3ae8","tid":46474,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:55:49.000Z","msg":"同我屋企差唔多<br />\n鬧交當食飯<br />\n依家更年期仲撚煩"},{"pid":"bf0f6221adb27e06682f03a48f308e4fb34ffa8b","tid":46474,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"我都唔知 總之佢可以因爲一件好小好小嘅事而發好大脾氣<br />\n試過我老豆放工訓教唔理我老母 佢都可以拉到話佢出面有第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4516ee5d210fea0e6ca695ad61d5960ddc717d03","tid":46474,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"以前我屋企都係咁，直到我出聲屌佢地兩個，就無再鬧交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}